messageBody:
All,

CodeNotes (a great book range) have a free download of their .NET book.
I have the Java and J2EE ones and I have found them a wealth of
information and all for a small cost ($19.95 USD).

The book can be found here:

http://www.codenotes.com/do/downloads/downloadsNETbook

Not sure if it's of any use but I have seen that quite a few people who
are using .NET...

Andy.

--
Andrew Beacock
Lammtara
